Package cdx.opencdx.protector.service

Interface OpenCDXProtectorService

All Known Implementing Classes:
OpenCDXProtectorServiceImpl
public interface OpenCDXProtectorService
Interface for the Protector Service.

This service provides methods for various security and protection functionalities. Implementations of this interface handle anomaly detection, authorization control, privacy protection, real-time monitoring, and user behavior analysis.
